Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空想だった感情が現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.59,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Ah！Cool！ You’re cool！Beautiful！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:23.30,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}平穏だった日常が乱雑に
